  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a journey to save the remnants of a cursed kingdom in Rogue Knight, an action-packed rogue-lite side-scrolling game that focuses on fast-paced combat and meaningful itemization. Gather resources to rebuild your town and obtain permanent upgrades. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/58d27b1056f5ee6549792c944489db27.gif?t=1732091635\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/58d27b1056f5ee6549792c944489db27.poster.avif?t=1732091635\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/49d3f327456be4b672ebd57c105c391d.poster.avif?t=1732091635\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/49d3f327456be4b672ebd57c105c391d.webm?t=1732091635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/49d3f327456be4b672ebd57c105c391d.mp4?t=1732091635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic combat combines melee with a diverse arsenal of spells.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/356abc30fbf20c97e6e2bbcd2722209b.poster.avif?t=1732091635\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/356abc30fbf20c97e6e2bbcd2722209b.webm?t=1732091635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/356abc30fbf20c97e6e2bbcd2722209b.mp4?t=1732091635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >World made with a mix of hand-crafted and procedurally generated content, providing variety while maintaining high quality. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/efdee87737dd11a8ec6e8431d005409a.webp?t=1732091635\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/efdee87737dd11a8ec6e8431d005409a.poster.avif?t=1732091635\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=200 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RPG-style itemization enables you to customize your character for your preferred playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/e5286d66e4104650c9ddb84fd2838180.poster.avif?t=1732091635\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/e5286d66e4104650c9ddb84fd2838180.webm?t=1732091635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/e5286d66e4104650c9ddb84fd2838180.mp4?t=1732091635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tough but fair combat with challenging boss fights.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a journey to save the remnants of a cursed kingdom in Rogue Knight, an action-packed rogue-lite side-scrolling game that focuses on fast-paced combat and meaningful itemization. Gather resources to rebuild your town and obtain permanent upgrades. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/58d27b1056f5ee6549792c944489db27.gif?t=1732091635\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/58d27b1056f5ee6549792c944489db27.poster.avif?t=1732091635\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/49d3f327456be4b672ebd57c105c391d.poster.avif?t=1732091635\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/49d3f327456be4b672ebd57c105c391d.webm?t=1732091635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/49d3f327456be4b672ebd57c105c391d.mp4?t=1732091635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic combat combines melee with a diverse arsenal of spells.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/356abc30fbf20c97e6e2bbcd2722209b.poster.avif?t=1732091635\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/356abc30fbf20c97e6e2bbcd2722209b.webm?t=1732091635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/356abc30fbf20c97e6e2bbcd2722209b.mp4?t=1732091635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >World made with a mix of hand-crafted and procedurally generated content, providing variety while maintaining high quality. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/efdee87737dd11a8ec6e8431d005409a.webp?t=1732091635\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/efdee87737dd11a8ec6e8431d005409a.poster.avif?t=1732091635\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=200 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RPG-style itemization enables you to customize your character for your preferred playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/e5286d66e4104650c9ddb84fd2838180.poster.avif?t=1732091635\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/e5286d66e4104650c9ddb84fd2838180.webm?t=1732091635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1318480/extras/e5286d66e4104650c9ddb84fd2838180.mp4?t=1732091635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tough but fair combat with challenging boss fights.</p>",
